	   <tr><td colspan=2>I just started an Heretic SK myself... <br><br>I put 10 points into Strength, 5 into Stamina (need the HP) and 5 more in AGI, as I believe also that Dex and Agi should at least be 75, and heck, Agi affects AC anyway... the Int should be plenty...<br><br>well, so far I am only level 6, and I should get level 7 staying in Toxx.&nbsp;&nbsp;I got lucky and while I was hunting in Paineel newbie area, someone wanted bone chips and was very generous with the payment, so I was able to afford a full set of leather early.  Once I hit 5 and hunted in Toxx, it seems pretty easy.  At 6 now, I can take on the full Kobold camps, and level pretty well that way, also going after the occasionnal skeleton or briar snake.  <br><br>My next questions would be: <br><br>1. Is it really feasable to stay on Odus until 9?  <br>2. Could I buy spells in the Bertox temple in Queynos sewers?  <br>3. How safe *is* the sewers, anyway? <br>4. Is our faction to the corrupt Queynos guards already high?<br>5. Can Erudites SK's visit the traditional evil towns of Neriak, Grobb, and Ogguk safely?  <br><br>And yes, travelling thru Erudin should be ok, as long as you don't veer off the main paths.  Just cover your head with a cloak, duck your eyes, and skedaddle through town...  <br><br>So I guess, depending on any answers to the above questions, I will go to Queynos soon, and hunt Gnolls for awhile... <br><br>Victus<br>Lvl 6 SK of Sol Ro server <br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
