	   <tr><td colspan=2>You are just dubious except to the cleric guilds.&nbsp;&nbsp;Luckily they stick in there temples praying like good lil priests should.  Head straight for docks and you will be safe.  Qeynos is another matter.  The guards there really dont like you.  Take the sewer entrance closest to the docks (almost under it) and then head through the catacombs to N Qeynos.  Get bound there, and head out to slay gnoll after gnoll (at least a hundred).  This should put you in good standings with the people of Qeynos.  After that you can do what ever you want (dont kill the bard unless you want to kill more gnolls).<br>&nbsp;<br>Iznoa, High Woman of Odus<br>Scribe of Erudin</td></tr>
